Telkomsel – D3 Customer Service Representative GRAPARI Telkomsel May 2014 | Indonesia Jobs Vacancies, Employment, Career Opportunities in Indonesia.
Jobs Vacancies, Employment And Career Opportunities in Indonesia.
05.01.2014 · Posted in
PT Telekomunikasi Selular – Telkomsel is the biggest cellular operator in Indonesia with maintains a total of 131.51 millions cellular subscribers at the end of 2013, both post paid and pre paid subscribers. Telkomsel also known as the widest cellular provider with operates more than 69,864 units of Base Transceiver Stations (BTS) throughout Indonesia or its network covering 95% of the population of Indonesia. Telkomsel is a subsidiary company of state-owned full-services telecommunications company PT Telekomunikasi Indonesia (Persero) Tbk or Telkom Group. By the end of 2013, Telkom Group holds 65% share in Telkomsel. Other 35% shares was owned by Singapore telecommunications giant Singapore Telecom Mobile Pte Ltd. According to
2013 Annual Report as cited by JobsCDC.com, PT Telekomunikasi Selular posted double digit growth in total assets. Telkomsel posted Rp73.33 trillion in the total assets as of December 2013, a 17 percent rise from Rp62.91 trillion in 2012.
Due to facing fast business growth and expanding of business across Indonesia,
care now looking for a person with strong motivation and goodwill to fill this position (work under authorized agency PT Infomedia Solusi Humanika by Telkom Indonesia)
Customer Service Representative (CSR)GRAPARI TELKOMSEL
Requirements
Female and Male.
Good looking and have a good personality.
Minimum height 160 cm (Female), 165 cm (Male).
Minimum education : 3 years of diploma program (D3) or equivalent, minimum GPA of 2.75.
Maximum age 25 years old at initial selection
Friendly, and customer oriented
Have a good communication skills
Familiar with Computer applications, minimum Microsoft Office and Internet
Placements : Balikpapan, Samarinda, Bontang and Tarakan
For further information, please refer official source from PT Infomedia Solusi Humanika by Telkom Indonesia on following link below. Should you are interested and qualified, please send your complete applications to the nearest GRAPARI Telkomsel at Balikpapan, Samarinda, Bontang and Tarakan or via email insanikalimantan@gmail.com. All applications will be treated in strict confidential and only use for the purpose of selection. All applications are appreciated and will be treated confidentially. (JobsCDC.com / )
